      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Abu Ali Al Ashary, from Muhammad Bin Abdul Jabbar, from Safwan Bin Yahya, from Khazr, from Muhammad Bin Muslim, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The one who is prejudicial, Allah<sup>azwj</sup> would Join him with a gang from the Fire’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "4. Abu Ali al-Ash’ari has narrated from Muhammad ibn ‘Abd al-Jabbar from Safwan ibn Yahya from Khudr from Muhammad ibn Muslim from abu ‘Abd Allah (a.s.) who has said the following: “On the Day of Judgment Allah will join those who practice racial discrimination with a race in fire.” "
        ]
      }
